  • 类
    说明
    ConsoleRunner
     
    Deamon
    A class to start a deamon thread for main
    GUIRunner
     
    RunMethod
    RunMethod declares the method that you may use in a deamon process
    The methods contains RunMethod.GUI and RunMethod.CONSOLE
    For RunMethod.GUI, the output of deamon info will be shown in a window
    For RunMethod.CONSOLE, the output will be printed as log (in this project)
